org.magnos.asset
Interface AssetFormat

All Known Implementing Classes:
AudioFormat, BaseAssetFormat, ClassFormat, CsvFormat, DatFormat, FontFormat, GifFormat, GzipFormat, ImageFormat, JarFormat, JsonFormat, MidiFormat, PropertyFormat, TextFormat, XmlFormat, ZipFormat
public interface AssetFormat

The format of an asset. A format will create the asset from an input stream and an optionally supplied asset info.

Author:
Philip Diffenderfer
